 * ExpandedChat Component (v3 - Wrapper)
 *
 * This component now wraps UnifiedChatContainer to provide the 4-column layout
 * with proper orchestration integration.
 *
 * @deprecated Implementation moved to UnifiedChatContainer.tsx
